OL,3,CThousands of Asian hornet queens
OL,4,Ccaught in Channel Islands this year
OL,6,FNearly 3,000 Asian hornet queens have
OL,7,Fbeen captured in Jersey so far this
OL,8,Fyear, with nearly 200 caught in
OL,9,FGuernsey and Herm over the last 10
OL,10,Fweeks alone.
OL,12,FAsian hornets are an invasive species
OL,13,Fwhich prey on other native insects,
OL,14,Fincluding honey bees and wasps, which
OL,15,Fcan have a devastating effect on
OL,16,Fbiodiversity.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
