OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781878275
OL,3,CThousands of Asian hornet queens
OL,4,Ccaught in Channel Islands this year
OL,6,FPeople in both Bailiwicks are being
OL,7,Fencouraged to track rather than trap
OL,8,Fthe hornets so local authorities can
OL,9,Flearn more about their behaviour and
OL,10,Fhow to prevent them from building
OL,11,Fnests.
OL,13,FNow figures from the islands' Asian
OL,14,FHornet organisations have revealed
OL,15,Fthat they are already seeing hundreds
OL,16,Fof nests across the Channel Islands.
OL,18,FThe Jersey Asian Hornet Group says
OL,19,Fthis time last year (2025), they had
OL,20,F1,374 reported queens and 152 nests.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781878275
OL,3,CThousands of Asian hornet queens
OL,4,Ccaught in Channel Islands this year
OL,6,FIt means that reported queens are now
OL,7,Fat double last year's rate.
OL,9,FFigures from the Jersey Asian Hornet
OL,10,FGroup for 2026 as of Friday 19 June:
OL,12,F*Of these, 2,715 have been caught and
OL,13,Fkilled.
OL,15,FFigures from the Asian Hornet Team -
OL,16,FGuernsey for the 10 weeks leading up
OL,17,Fto Monday 15 June:
OL,19,FIn 2025, 694 nests were discovered in
OL,20,FJersey, with 71 found in Guernsey.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781878275
OL,3,CThousands of Asian hornet queens
OL,4,Ccaught in Channel Islands this year
OL,6,FIn Guernsey, islanders are being asked
OL,7,Fto report the location of any hornets
OL,8,Fthey see, the direction it is flying,
OL,9,Fand to take a photo if it is safe to
OL,10,Fdo so.
OL,12,FGovernment advice in Jersey also
OL,13,Fsuggests that anyone working outside
OL,14,Fshould be wary of Asian hornet nests,
OL,15,Fwhich can start out being the size of
OL,16,Fa tennis ball but grow to be the size
OL,17,Fof a football by late July.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781878275
OL,3,CThousands of Asian hornet queens
OL,4,Ccaught in Channel Islands this year
OL,6,FIt is advised that islanders stay at
OL,7,Fleast 10 metres away from any nests
OL,8,Fthey find and should not touch,
OL,9,Fdisturb or cause vibrations around
OL,10,Fnests.
OL,12,FNests are usually found high in trees
OL,13,Fbut may also be uncovered in brambles,
OL,14,Fhedges, garden sheds, roof spaces,
OL,15,Fcliffs and even in the ground.
OL,17,FAsian hornets can sometimes be
OL,18,Fmistaken for European hornets, which
OL,19,Fare native to the Channel Islands.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
