CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781878275
OL,3,CThousands of Asian hornet queens
OL,4,Ccaught in Channel Islands this year
OL,6,FAnne Lotte, from the Guernsey Asian
OL,7,FHornet Team, says: "Asian hornets have
OL,8,Fa black body with a large orange
OL,9,Fstripe on the back and two smaller
OL,10,Fyellow bands.
OL,12,F"Their legs are half yellow and half
OL,13,Fblack, and they have a very
OL,14,Fdistinctive orange face."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781878275
OL,3,CThousands of Asian hornet queens
OL,4,Ccaught in Channel Islands this year
OL,6,FAnne says that Jersey usually sees
OL,7,Fmore hornets each year because it's
OL,8,Fcloser to France, explaining: "We know
OL,9,Fthe Asian hornet is very well
OL,10,Festablished (in France), so there will
OL,11,Fbe yearly occurrences of Asian hornets
OL,12,Fflying into Jersey.
OL,14,F"Another reason is that last year,
OL,15,FJersey had more nests, meaning they
OL,16,Fhad more Asian hornets as well, and it
OL,17,Fis possible that they've missed more
OL,18,Fnests and that these queens hibernate
OL,19,Fin the island and then create new
OL,20,Fnests.
OL,26,@rD@MpmrD@Wpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781878275
OL,3,CThousands of Asian hornet queens
OL,4,Ccaught in Channel Islands this year
OL,6,FAnne says they are "very confident"
OL,7,Fthat Guernsey is on top of dealing
OL,8,Fwith the island's invasive hornet
OL,9,Fpopulation.
OL,11,F"We have a very good strategy, which
OL,12,Fhas two distinct phases. One is the
OL,13,Fspring queening, where we trap all the
OL,14,Fqueens, and this stops them from
OL,15,Fmaking their nests.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781878275
OL,3,CThousands of Asian hornet queens
OL,4,Ccaught in Channel Islands this year
OL,6,F"Then, our second phase is to track
OL,7,Fdown and trample, which is the phase
OL,8,Fwe're going into now. That's where we
OL,9,Factively try to find these Asian
OL,10,Fhornets and see where they're flying
OL,11,Fto, find their direction, their flight
OL,12,Flines and then locate their nests.
OL,14,F"Once we've found a nest, we do
OL,15,Feverything we can for a rapid removal
OL,16,Fof the nest."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
